_sText:
Edited, refreshed version of mg_dream_xmas_edition_final. Lights, cubemaps, fitted textures, texture/geometry adjustments and optimizations, small tweaks, etc

I only merely edited the original map, I did not create it.

This edit is also a few years old, so if you already have it on your server, you don't need to download it again. I'm only putting it here so other people have a chance to see it.

Original version can be found here: http://gamebanana.com/maps/170260
